flowchart TD
    A([Change Request]) --> A1[/Documentation Gate 1:\nRequester submits RFC with\nSOX control mapping/]
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Documentation Gate 1 & Compliance Check
    A1 --> A2{SOX Compliance\nPre-Check}
    A2 --> |Pass| B{Emergency?}
    A2 --> |Fail| A3[Return for SOX\nRemediation]
    A3 --> A1
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION
    B --> |Yes| C[Emergency CAB]
    B --> |No| D[Standard Review]
    C --> E[Expedited Approval]
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX checkpoint for emergency path
    E --> E1{SOX Emergency\nWaiver Approved?}
    E1 --> |Yes| H[Schedule Change Window]
    E1 --> |No| D
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION
    D --> F[Weekly CAB Meeting]
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Documentation Gate 2 before CAB
    D --> D1[/Documentation Gate 2:\nRisk Assessment &\nSOX Impact Analysis/]
    D1 --> F
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION
    F --> G{Approved?}
    G --> |Yes| H
    G --> |No| I[Return to Requester]
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX Segregation of Duties check
    H --> H1{SOX SoD Check:\nImplementer ≠ Approver?}
    H1 --> |Yes| J[Implementation]
    H1 --> |No| H2[Reassign Implementer\nper SoD Policy]
    H2 --> J
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION
    J --> K{Successful?}
    K --> |Yes| L[Post-Impl Review]
    K --> |No| M1[Execute Backout Plan]
    M1 --> M2{Backout Successful?}
    M2 --> |Yes| M3[Document Backout & Reschedule]
    M2 --> |No| M[Incident Report]
    M3 --> N
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - SOX Audit Documentation Gate & Final Compliance
    L --> L1[/Documentation Gate 3:\nEvidence Collection &\nAudit Trail Finalization/]
    L1 --> L2{SOX Post-Impl\nCompliance Review}
    L2 --> |Compliant| N([Close Change])
    L2 --> |Non-Compliant| L3[SOX Finding Report\n& Remediation Plan]
    L3 --> N
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION
    M --> N

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - RACI Role Labels
    A -.-> |R: Requester\nA: Change Manager| A
    D -.-> |R: Change Manager\nA: CAB Chair\nC: SOX Compliance Officer\nI: Requester| D
    F -.-> |R: CAB Chair\nA: IT Director\nC: SOX Compliance Officer\nI: Stakeholders| F
    J -.-> |R: Implementer\nA: Change Manager\nC: SOX Compliance Officer\nI: Requester| J
    L -.-> |R: Change Manager\nA: IT Director\nC: SOX Auditor\nI: Requester| L
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Styling
    style A1 fill:#FFD700,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style D1 fill:#FFD700,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style L1 fill:#FFD700,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style A2 fill:#FF6B6B,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style E1 fill:#FF6B6B,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style H1 fill:#FF6B6B,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style L2 fill:#FF6B6B,stroke:#333,color:#000
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION

