%% CLAUDE'S CHANGE INTERPRETATION
%% ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
%% OBJECTIVE: Ensure change management process meets SOX audit requirements by embedding mandatory compliance checkpoints, segregation of duties validation, documentation gates, and RACI accountability at each critical stage.
%%
%% EXPLANATION:
%% Added three Documentation Gates (RFC submission with SOX mapping, Risk Assessment & SOX Impact Analysis before CAB, and Evidence Collection & Audit Trail before closure). Inserted SOX compliance checkpoints: a pre-check after submission, an emergency waiver gate for expedited changes, a Segregation of Duties verification before implementation, and a post-implementation compliance review. Added RACI role annotations (Responsible, Accountable, Consulted, Informed) as dotted links on key process nodes. Applied color styling to distinguish documentation gates (gold) from compliance checkpoints (red) for visual clarity.
%% ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
